几天后，另一股热带扰动沿中美洲和墨西哥南海岸向西平行移动，对流开始逐渐组织起来，系统于6月19日晚在墨西哥[[曼萨尼约|曼萨尼约]]西南偏南方向约420公里洋面发展成第二{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压。成为热带低气压时，气旋保持着大规模且拉长的下层环流，并带有部分带状特征，但外流由于[[风切变|风切变]]的影响而受到限制。美国国家飓风中心起初预测低气压会增强，达到风力时速80公里强度，但也有两个[[热带气旋预报模型|计算机模型]]预计气旋会很快消散。由于受到墨西哥上空高压脊的影响，低气压向西北偏西方向移动，<ref name="td2edisc1">{{cite web | author = Guiney & Avila | year = 1998 | title = Tropical Depression Two-E Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021004632/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP0298.001 | accessdate = 2014-09-06 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP0298.001 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no }}</ref>同时也因风切变不断增多而无法得到显著发展。到了6月20日，环流中心已经部分暴露出来，并且位置也在大部分对流的东北方向，这表明风暴的强度较弱。低气压一度接近热带风暴强度<ref name="td2edisc5">{{cite web | author = Avila | year = 1998 | title = Tropical Depression Two-E Discussion Five | publisher = National Hurricane Center | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021004640/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP0298.005 | accessdate = 2014-09-06 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP0298.005 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref>，但其中的深层对流在系统进入水温较低的海域后消退。6月21日，美国国家飓风中心发布了针对低气压的最后一份公告，称低气压虽然仍保有层次分明的下层环流，但已经没有关联的对流存在<ref name="td2edisc10">{{cite web | author = Mayfield | year = 1998 | title = Tropical Depression Two-E Discussion Ten | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-09-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021004645/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP0298.010 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP0298.010 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。墨西哥西南部部分地区因这场风暴出现暴雨，局部最高降雨量达到141毫米<ref>{{cite web | author = David M. Roth | year = 2009 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130927012415/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/td02eof1998filledrainblk.gif | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/td02eof1998filledrainblk.gif | title = Tropical Depression 2E (1998) Storm Total Rainfall Graphic | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2014-09-06 | archivedate = 2013-09-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。
