一股热带扰动天气发展出持续的对流，并关联有下层环流，于10月1日在墨西哥曼萨尼约西北偏西方向约565公里洋面组织成第十二{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压。由于位处一片存在弱转向气流的海域，气象学家起初预计系统会向西北偏西方向缓慢行进，并且风速会达到每小时95公里左右，但气旋实际上却是向东飘移，之后再缓慢朝西掉头。<ref name="td12disc1">{{cite web | author = Guiney | year = 1998 | title = Tropical Depression Twelve-E Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-09-07 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1298.001 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019020526/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1298.001 | deadurl = no | 9 =  | archivedate = 2012-10-19 }}</ref><ref name="12tcr">{{cite web | author = Guiney | year = 1998 | title = Tropical Depression Twelve-E Best Track | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-09-07 | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102214952/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/1998td12e.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/1998td12e.html }}</ref>低气压未能进一步组织起来，其外观也逐渐恶化。10月2日清晨，有两艘船只报告系统北面更远的地方出现西南风，美国国家飓风中心因此认定这时的气旋中心要么非常小，要么就根本不存在，或是中心位置在[[雷暴|雷暴]]活动以北较远的位置。该组织在实际操作中把风暴中心向北面调整<ref name="td12disc3">{{cite web | author = Rappaport | year = 1998 | title = Tropical Depression Twelve-E Discussion Three | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-09-07 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1298.003 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019020540/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1298.003 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-19 }}</ref>，并在6小时后根据可以辨识的卫星图像将中心位置向南调整了185公里<ref name="td12disc4">{{cite web | author = Lawrence | year = 1998 | title = Tropical Depression Twelve-E Discussion Four | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-09-07 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1298.004 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019020557/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1298.004 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-19 }}</ref>，此后又在发布针对系统的最后一份公告时再次向北移动。到了10月3日清晨，低气压中已经只有时断时续的对流存在<ref name="td12disc6">{{cite web | author = Avila | year = 1998 | title = Tropical Depression Twelve-E Discussion Six | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-09-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019020649/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1298.006 | archivedate = 2012-10-19 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1298.006 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，于同日晚些时间在下加利福尼亚半岛方向消散<ref name="12tcr" />。气旋东部边缘令墨西哥西南部普降暴雨，局部降雨量最高的达到161毫米<ref>{{cite web | author = David M. Roth | year = 2009 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/td12eof1998filledrainblk.gif | title = Tropical Depression 12E (1998) Storm Total Rainfall Graphic | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130925113216/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/td12eof1998filledrainblk.gif | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-09-25 | accessdate = 2014-09-07 }}</ref>。
